  "text": "## Complaint Prevention Tips  \n**To Avoid Issues:**\n1. **Verify details** before making transfers (account number, sort code)\n2. **Keep records** of all communications\n3. **Monitor your account** regularly for unauthorized activity\n4. **Report issues quickly** — don't wait weeks\n5. **Use secure passwords** and enable 2FA\n6. **Ask questions** if something seems wrong  \n---",
